      "main_description_html": "<h2 dir=\"auto\">Epic A — Auth · Login (/login)</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Slice the full-page Login design — also builds the shared two-column auth layout (brand/benefits panel + form card) reused by Signup.</p>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Scope</h3>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Two-column layout; left brand panel (headline, 3 points, quote), right form card.</li>\n<li>Email, password with show/hide toggle, \"Keep me signed in\", \"Forgot password?\", Continue, divider, Google button, \"Sign up\" link.</li>\n<li>Light + dark; responsive (stacks on mobile). Markup only.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Acceptance criteria</h3>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Matches the new Login design in both themes, all breakpoints.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Testing scenario (QA)</h3>\n<ol dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Compare /login to Login.html on desktop &amp; mobile.</li>\n<li>Toggle password show/hide → input type switches; icon updates.</li>\n<li>Dark mode → panel, card, inputs styled correctly.</li>\n<li>Mobile → columns stack; no overflow.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Demo by Developer</h2>\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"images/image-49a92e95-532b-40f6-a133-ab9d4ee53f95.png\"><img width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"images/image-49a92e95-532b-40f6-a133-ab9d4ee53f95.png\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 1080px;; aspect-ratio: 1920 / 1080; background-color: var(--bgColor-muted); border-radius: 6px\" class=\"js-gh-image-fallback\"></a>\n<p dir=\"auto\">🧪 QA Tester Summary — Issue <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4588209719\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1598\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1598/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1598\">#1598</a>: [Slicing] Login page (/login) — markup &amp; styles</p>