      "main_description_html": "<h2 dir=\"auto\">Epic: Contact page <code class=\"notranslate\">/contact</code> (slicing)</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Redesign <code class=\"notranslate\">ContactComponent</code> markup &amp; styles to match <code class=\"notranslate\">Contact.html</code>, inside <code class=\"notranslate\">.vm-marketing</code>.</p>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Scope</h3>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Page hero + breadcrumb; info aside (email, response time, help center, social).</li>\n<li>3-form accordion: 01 General Inquiries, 02 Help Center, 03 Custom Exhibition request.</li>\n<li>Field layouts, dropzones (visual), captcha placeholder, success-state markup.</li>\n<li>Light + dark; responsive.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Acceptance criteria</h3>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li><code class=\"notranslate\">/contact</code> matches the new design in both themes, all breakpoints; accordion expands/collapses.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Testing scenario (QA)</h3>\n<ol dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Compare <code class=\"notranslate\">/contact</code> against <code class=\"notranslate\">Contact.html</code> on desktop and mobile.</li>\n<li>Expand/collapse each of the 3 forms — only one open behaves per design.</li>\n<li>Toggle dark mode → forms, dropzones, captcha, success state styled correctly.</li>\n<li>Resize → field rows stack correctly on mobile.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Demo by Developer</h2>\n<details open=\"\" class=\"details-reset border rounded-2\">\n  <summary class=\"tmp-px-3 py-2\">\n    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" data-component=\"Octicon\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-device-camera-video\">\n    <path d=\"M16 3.75v8.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.136.643L11 10.575v.675A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 13h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 11.25v-6.5C0 3.784.784 3 1.75 3h7.5c.966 0 1.75.784 1.75 1.75v.675l3.864-2.318A.75.75 0 0 1 16 3.75Zm-6.5 1a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25h-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v6.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0