      "main_description_html": "<h2 dir=\"auto\">Epic: Shared shell — Footer (slicing)</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Redesign the markup &amp; styles of the shared footer (<code class=\"notranslate\">layouts/footer</code>) to the new design.</p>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Scope</h3>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Slice footer: brand/blurb, Product / Company / Legal link columns, social icons, copyright row.</li>\n<li>Light + dark styling; responsive.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Acceptance criteria</h3>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Footer matches the new design in both themes and all breakpoints.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Testing scenario (QA)</h3>\n<ol dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Compare footer against the new design on desktop and mobile.</li>\n<li>Toggle dark mode → footer styling correct.</li>\n<li>Resize → columns stack correctly on mobile.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Demo by Developer</h2>\n<details open=\"\" class=\"details-reset border rounded-2\">\n  <summary class=\"tmp-px-3 py-2\">\n    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" data-component=\"Octicon\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-device-camera-video\">\n    <path d=\"M16 3.75v8.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.136.643L11 10.575v.675A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 13h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 11.25v-6.5C0 3.784.784 3 1.75 3h7.5c.966 0 1.75.784 1.75 1.75v.675l3.864-2.318A.75.75 0 0 1 16 3.75Zm-6.5 1a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25h-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v6.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-6.5ZM11 8.825l3.5 2.1v-5.85l-3.5 2.1Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n    <span class=\"m-1\">2026-06-05.14-42-12.mp4</span>\n    <span class=\"dropdown-caret\"></span>\n  </summary>\n\n  <video src=\"videos/video-997a4cf7-cfe8-42f2-b759-f446df4561c9.mp4\" data-canonical-src=\"videos/video-997a4cf7-cfe8-42f2-b759-f446df4561c9.mp4\" controls=\"controls\" muted=\"muted\" class=\"d-block rounded-bottom-2 border-top width-fit\" style=\"max-height:640px; min-height: 200px\">\n\n  </video>\n</details>\n\n<p dir=\"auto\">