      "display_title": "Issue #1559: [Slicing] Shared header — markup & styles",
      "main_description_html": "<h2 dir=\"auto\">Epic: Shared shell — Header (slicing)</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Redesign the markup &amp; styles of the shared header (<code class=\"notranslate\">layouts/header</code>) to the new design.</p>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Scope</h3>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Slice the new nav: brand mark, primary links, theme-toggle button, Log in / Get started buttons.</li>\n<li>Responsive layout (desktop + mobile/hamburger).</li>\n<li>Light + dark styling using shell tokens.</li>\n<li>Markup only — feature wiring is a separate task.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Acceptance criteria</h3>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Header visually matches the new design in both themes, all breakpoints.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Testing scenario (QA)</h3>\n<ol dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Compare header against the new design (<code class=\"notranslate\">Villume.html</code> nav) on desktop and mobile.</li>\n<li>Toggle dark mode → header colors/contrast correct.</li>\n<li>Resize to mobile → nav collapses correctly; no overflow.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Demo by Developer</h2>\n<details open=\"\" class=\"details-reset border rounded-2\">\n  <summary class=\"tmp-px-3 py-2\">\n    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" data-component=\"Octicon\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-device-camera-video\">\n    <path d=\"M16 3.75v8.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.136.643L11 10.575v.675A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 13h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 11.25v-6.5C0 3.784.784 3 1.75 3h7.5c.966 0 1.75.784 1.75 1.75v.675l3.864-2.318A.75.75 0 0 1 16 3.75Zm-6.5 1a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25h-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v6.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-6.5ZM11 8.825l3.5 2.1v-5.85l-3.5 2.1Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n    <span class=\"m-1\">2026-06-05.14-45-29.mp4</span>\n    <span class=\"dropdown-caret\"></span>\n  </summary>\n\n  <video src=\"videos/video-92738f31-5338-4009-b779-9f9c253c644d.mp4\" data-canonical-src=\"videos/video-92738f31-5338-4009-b779